OL,3,CLeave granted for judicial review into
OL,4,Cinstalling Irish signage at station
OL,6,FLoyalist activist Jamie Bryson has
OL,7,Fsecured High Court permission to
OL,8,Fchallenge plans to have Irish language
OL,9,Fsignage installed at Grand Central
OL,10,FStation in Belfast.
OL,12,FHe was granted leave to seek a
OL,13,Fjudicial review into Sinn Fein
OL,14,FInfrastructure Minister Liz Kimmins'
OL,15,Fdecision to approve the #150,000
OL,16,Fscheme at the city's new public
OL,17,Ftransport hub.
