OL,3,CLeave granted for judicial review into
OL,4,Cinstalling Irish signage at station
OL,6,FA judge ruled on Friday that Mr Bryson
OL,7,Fhas established an arguable case the
OL,8,Fmove was so controversial that it
OL,9,Frequired agreement from the entire
OL,10,FStormont Executive.
OL,12,FMr Justice Scoffield listed the case
OL,13,Ffor a full hearing in September.
OL,15,FProceedings were issued after Ms
OL,16,FKimmins announced in March that Irish
OL,17,Fsignage is to be installed at Grand
OL,18,FCentral and on ticket vending machines.
