OL,6,FFurther correspondence from UUP, TUV,
OL,7,FPUP and Orange Order representatives
OL,8,Fto back Mr Bryson's claims of unionist
OL,9,Funity on the issue.
OL,11,FHe insisted that the challenge clearly
OL,12,Fcrossed the legal standard for the
OL,13,Fdecision to be subjected to further
OL,14,Fjudicial scrutiny.
OL,16,F"We have the Deputy First Minister of
OL,17,Fthe country saying this is
OL,18,Fcontroversial... and Mr Robinson could
OL,19,Fnot be clearer that the views of his
OL,20,Fministers and party are that this is
OL,21,Fcontroversial," he submitted.
