OL,6,F"For the purpose of obtaining leave
OL,7,F(to apply for judicial review) this
OL,8,Fpole vaults over the threshold."
OL,10,FDisputing that assessment, Counsel for
OL,11,Fthe Minister said a TUV petition in
OL,12,Fthe Assembly against the dual language
OL,13,Fsignage attracted no signatures of
OL,14,Fsupport from any other MLAs.
OL,16,FTony McGleenan KC told the court that
OL,17,Fthe mechanism deployed by Timothy
OL,18,FGaston in an attempt to have the issue
OL,19,Freferred to the Executive "registered
OL,20,Fa nil return".
