OL,6,FHe contended: "Taking the most
OL,7,Frelevant indicator, and the one
OL,8,Fenshrined in statute, the outcome is
OL,9,Fthat there isn't a flicker of
OL,10,Fcontroversy about this."
OL,12,FBut according to Mr Bryson, the
OL,13,Fpetition could not have achieved
OL,14,Fanything more than a discussion about
OL,15,Fthe planned Irish signage.
OL,17,FMr Justice Scoffield was told that the
OL,18,Fissue has already been raised at an
OL,19,FExecutive meeting last month under any
OL,20,Fother business.
